menu_jobunitlist
[TITLE]The Manual:  Job/Unit List[/TITLE]
[C:7:0:1]How to Get Here[C:7:0:0]
[B]
Press [IKEY:D_JOBLIST] or Press [IKEY:D_UNITLIST] from the main view.  The first emphasizes jobs and the
second emphasizes units.
[B][B]
[C:7:0:1]Description[C:7:0:0]
[B]
This screen is a convenient way to few which tasks are active in the fortress and what your dwarves are doing.
Use [IKEY:STANDARDSCROLL_UP][IKEY:STANDARDSCROLL_DOWN][IKEY:STANDARDSCROLL_PAGEUP][IKEY:STANDARDSCROLL_PAGEDOWN] to scroll.
[B]
You can view the particulars of the job or unit profiles from this screen.
[B]
[LINK:data/help/unit_profile]Unit Profiles[/LINK]
[B]
You can also zoom to units or related buildings, or remove a unit from certain jobs.
[B]
If you have a manager, you can access the manager screen from here.
[B]
[LINK:data/help/menu_manager]Manager Screen[/LINK]
